description: Sends a CIS session telemetry. This API is used by the Amazon Inspector SSM plugin to communicate with the Amazon Inspector service. The Amazon Inspector SSM plugin calls this API to start a CIS scan session for the scan ID supplied by the service.

parameters.name: messages
parameters.description: The CIS session telemetry messages. (dict) --- The CIS session message. The CIS rule details for the CIS session message. The rule ID for the CIS session message. The status of the CIS session message.

nested_params.name: cisRuleDetails
nested_params.description: The CIS rule details for the CIS session message.

nested_params.name: ruleId
nested_params.description: The rule ID for the CIS session message.

nested_params.name: status
nested_params.description: The status of the CIS session message.

parameters.name: scanJobId
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the scan job.

parameters.name: sessionToken
parameters.description: The unique token that identifies the CIS session.
